---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Now";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} isGallery={false}>
  <div class="text-center">
    <p class="mb-5 font-semibold text-lg text-themeGray-800 text-center">
      I don't remember where I first saw it, but someone out there on the
      internet had a page for what they're currently working on, called the Now
      page. Last updated 8/25/2025.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-3 font-normal text-lg text-themeGray-800">
      My day job is that of a Power Platform Developer. That entails low-code
      configuration, and pro-code work in JavaScript, TypeScript, and C#.
    </p>

    <p class="pb-3 font-normal text-lg text-themeGray-800">
      In my free time, I'm working on a website that is planned to be a one-stop
      shop for learning photography.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
